high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Pick up the glass from the sink.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Heat the glass and then pick up the glass again.
Turn right and face the sink.
Put the glass in the cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated glass in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the cup from the right sink basin.
Turn around and walk over to the microwave that is now on your right.
Place the cup on the plate in the microwave and heat it before pulling the cup back out.
Turn to the right and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Open the cabinet that is directly below the left hand side of the sink and place the cup inside.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup into a cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the fridge
pick up a cup from the sink
move to the microwave to the left of the sink
heat the cup in the microwave
move to the cabinet to the left of the sink
put the cup in the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put a heated cup in the cabinet under the sink.
